---
const SEGMENTS_URL =
  "https://spoke.withtheranks.com/docs/spoke-admin/segments_and_encodings/";
---

<section class="bg-white px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24 lg:px-8 lg:py-32" id="pricing">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-[960px] flex-col gap-16">
    <div class="text-[#1c1c1c]">
      <h2 class="font-display text-5xl leading-none sm:text-6xl lg:text-[90px]">The most affordable way to text.</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 font-sans text-xl leading-normal sm:text-2xl">
        <p>
          With the Ranks strives to offer the lowest texting rates in the industry, negotiating bulk rate discounts on
          behalf of our users and maintaining a transparent pricing structure that supports ongoing development and
          support of the platform.
        </p>
        <p class="font-bold">We only charge for texts you send.</p>
        <p>
          We don’t charge for setup, inbound message, 10DLC registration, landline filtering, or technical support —
          just pay-as-you go, per message segment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
      <div
        class="rounded-2xl border-4 border-[#1c1c1c] bg-[linear-gradient(-58deg,#ffefc0_0.36%,#fac328_99.64%)] p-8 font-sans text-[#1c1c1c]"
      >
        <p class="mb-2 text-2xl sm:text-3xl">
          <span class="font-bold">1.3¢</span>
          <span> </span>
          <span class="text-xl sm:text-2xl">per outbound SMS segment</span>
        </p>
        <p class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl">
          <span class="font-bold">3.25¢</span>
          <span> </span>
          <span class="text-xl sm:text-2xl">per outbound MMS message</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <a
        class="link-inline-external-icon group font-sans text-2xl font-bold text-[#1c1c1c] no-underline"
        href={SEGMENTS_URL}
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
      >
        <span class="group-hover:underline">Learn more about message segments</span><i
          class="iconoir-arrow-up-right-square-solid text-2xl leading-none text-cta-end"
          aria-hidden="true"
        ></i></a>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded bg-brand-ink px-6 py-12 text-white sm:px-8 sm:py-16">
      <h3 class="font-display text-5xl leading-none sm:text-6xl lg:text-[64px]">Bulk Discounts</h3>
      <div class="mt-4 max-w-[960px] font-sans text-xl leading-normal sm:text-2xl">
        <p>Planning on sending a lot of texts? We offer bulk discounts, and your commitments will help lower prices for everyone.</p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Reach out to{" "}
          <a class="font-bold text-[#ffefc0] underline decoration-[#fac328]" href="mailto:hello@withtheranks.com">
            hello@withtheranks.com
          </a>{" "}
          for more information.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
